Name: Jetpack Dog
About the game: In this game you have to visit the dog, which the hosts left at home. But everything is not so bad, under the mat he hides a jetpack and all you need is to collect your favorite bones and not get under the laser! Features: The game is in the style of the Endless runner; Dynamic soundtrack; Lovely dog; A huge number of bones; Funny drawing.
